264
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,791
So there's nothing
to fight about, right?

265
00:16:30,875 --> 00:16:32,541
It's way too late for excuses.

266
00:16:32,625 --> 00:16:34,791
Tomo's here
to settle the score

267
00:16:34,875 --> 00:16:37,416
with that blond
black magic bimbo.

268
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:41,500
