so I'll go first.

269
00:16:41,583 --> 00:16:44,291
Poyonyo poyo poyo switcheroo!

270
00:16:44,375 --> 00:16:45,583
Turtle!

271
00:16:45,666 --> 00:16:46,333
What the--?!

272
00:16:46,416 --> 00:16:47,125
What is that?

273
00:16:47,208 --> 00:16:49,458
But wait! There's more!

274
00:16:50,541 --> 00:16:51,708
Snake!

275
00:16:51,791 --> 00:16:53,333
Switcheroo!

276
00:16:53,416 --> 00:16:54,833
Crayfish!

277
00:16:54,916 --> 00:16:56,583
Listen up, you monsters.

278
00:16:56,666 --> 00:16:58,500
The great and mighty
Tomo commands you

279
00:16:58,583 --> 00:17:02,416
to mop up the floor
with that blond witchy girl.

280
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:03,750
Snake.

281
00:17:03,833 --> 00:17:04,833
Crayfish!

282
00:17:04,916 --> 00:17:06,541
Turtle!

283
00:17:07,458 --> 00:17:09,125
This is nuts.

284
00:17:09,208 --> 00:17:10,416
You're amazing Tomoka!

285
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:11,708
And so subtle...

286
00:17:11,791 --> 00:17:14,708
Cease fire, monster troops.

287
00:17:15,458 --> 00:17:16,416
