290
00:17:21,833 --> 00:17:22,750
Take her down!

291
00:17:22,833 --> 00:17:25,416
Hit her with
everything you got!

292
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:26,125
Turtle!

293
00:17:26,208 --> 00:17:26,875
Crayfish!

294
00:17:26,958 --> 00:17:28,500
Snake!

295
00:17:28,583 --> 00:17:29,791
