would have fighting monsters?

298
00:17:41,708 --> 00:17:43,500
I think it's about
time you learn what happens

299
00:17:43,583 --> 00:17:46,291
to those who
dare to oppose me.

300
00:17:46,375 --> 00:17:49,583
