the power of the netherworld!

301
00:18:31,875 --> 00:18:33,750
Nya nyo? Nya!

302
00:18:33,833 --> 00:18:38,083
[FUKUYAMA giggles pervertedly]

303
00:18:38,166 --> 00:18:39,583
So this is where
you've been hiding,

304
00:18:39,666 --> 00:18:41,208
