305
00:18:41,291 --> 00:18:44,083
Now bask in the
warmth of my love!

306
00:18:45,625 --> 00:18:47,708
Watch the hair!

307
00:18:50,291 --> 00:18:52,750
Ebi! Stop playing hard to get!

308
00:18:52,833 --> 00:18:54,166
