314
00:19:08,833 --> 00:19:11,958
No! It's all my fault!

315
00:19:21,958 --> 00:19:23,916
[LISA crying]

316
00:19:27,583 --> 00:19:29,625
Nya Nya...

317
00:19:33,666 --> 00:19:35,583
Nya?

318
00:19:35,666 --> 00:19:37,083
Oh, Ebi.

319
00:19:37,166 --> 00:19:39,000
Thank goodness you're okay.

320
00:19:39,083 --> 00:19:41,208
But how? How'd you survive?

321
00:19:41,291 --> 00:19:44,208
