326
00:19:55,333 --> 00:19:57,375
and there's
nothing to be afraid of,

327
00:19:57,458 --> 00:19:59,166
so relax and let's
have ourselves some fun.

328
00:19:59,250 --> 00:20:01,625
There's no time
like the present!

329
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,791
Go do it in Hell!

330
00:20:08,041 --> 00:20:10,416
That a girl, Tomoka.

331
00:20:21,375 --> 00:20:23,458
Ellie.

332
00:20:29,291 --> 00:20:31,250
[ELLIE barks]

333
00:20:36,416 --> 00:20:40,375
