343
00:21:13,625 --> 00:21:16,458
You won, fair and square,
and the match is over.

344
00:21:16,541 --> 00:21:19,916
So Blondie and Tomo
are friends now.

345
00:21:20,458 --> 00:21:23,125
You know, the TV
isn't always right...

346
00:21:23,208 --> 00:21:28,583
But...

347
00:21:28,666 --> 00:21:30,666
If you really wanna
be friends with me,

348
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:34,500
I guess it would be kinda
neat to have you as one.

349
00:21:36,041 --> 00:21:37,833
[ELLIE barks]

350
00:21:39,250 --> 00:21:41,750
You're glad it
worked out. Me too.

351
00:21:41,833 --> 00:21:43,958
Nya nyaa! Nya nya nyuu!
Nya nyu nya nyu...!

352
00:21:44,041 --> 00:21:46,833
Hey, come on, that tickles!

353
00:21:48,291 --> 00:21:49,541
[TOMO] I know!

354
00:21:49,625 --> 00:21:51,375
You should come over to
our house and watch Poyon!

355
00:21:51,458 --> 00:21:52,375
[LISA] When is it on?

356
00:21:52,458 --> 00:21:54,333
Don't worry, I recorded it!

